elarus U-17]] |- |[[FMF Cup 2011|2011]] |{{flagicon|AZE}} [[Azerbaijan national under-17 football team|Azerbaijan U-17]] |* |{{flagicon|MDA}} [[Moldova national under-17 football team|Moldova U-17]] |- |[[FMF Cup 2012|2012]] |{{flagicon|ROU}} [[Romania national under-17 football team|Romania U-17]] |* |{{flagicon|AZE}} [[Azerbaijan national under-17 football team|Azerbaijan U-17]] |}
