The '''Flanders Indoor Cyclo-cross''' is a [[cyclo-cross]] race held in the [[Nekkerhal]] in [[Mechelen]], [[Belgium]]. It is the first ever indoor cyclo-cross race, which was held for the first time on 17 January 2007.

